query:
-- Get islands without atollId
SELECT p.id, p.name, p.slug, p.latitude, p.longitude
FROM places p
WHERE p.type = 'island' AND p.atollId IS NULL
ORDER BY p.name
LIMIT 20;

-- Check if there's any pattern in the data
SELECT COUNT(*) as total_islands_without_atoll FROM places WHERE type = 'island' AND atollId IS NULL;
